        <div data-id="trello-icebox" data-view="Number" data-title="Icebox" class="purple"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12"></div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-3" id="wunderlist">
        <div class="measurement-header">
          <h3 class="measurement-title">TODOs</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            <p class="goal">Zero</p>
            <p>The TODOs widget monitors how many tasks are due on that day.</p>
            <p>I use <a href="https://wunderlist.com">Wunderlist</a> to track small tasks only (eg 'going to the post office').</p>
            <p class="code"><a href="https://gist.github.com/camilleldn/1092f66251ad1461b473">Code for widget</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-3" id="email">
        <div class="measurement-header">
          <h3 class="measurement-title">Email</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          <p class="goal">Zero</p>
          <p>The email widget monitors how many emails are currently in my inbox.</p>
          <p>I manage regular subscriptions with <a href="http://unroll.me">Unroll.me</a> so I only get one email per day for subscription emails.</p>
          <p class="code"><a href="https://gist.github.com/camilleldn/10709a0ec6b25323f1cb">Code for widget</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-3" id="newsletter">
        <div class="measurement-header">
          <h3 class="measurement-title">Newsletter</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          <p class="goal">Every month</p>
          <p>I keep in touch with a few of my close friends by writing a monthly-ish newsletter, featuring bad puns and terrible doodles.</p>
          <p class="code"><a href="https://gist.github.com/hannesfostie/5420959">Code for widget</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-sm-3" id="blog">
        <div class="measurement-header">
          <h3 class="measurement-title">Blog</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
          <p class="goal">Every month</p>
          <p>I write the occasional technical blog post on <a href="http://camillebaldock.com">my website</a>.</p>
          <p class="code"><a href="https://gist.github.com/hannesfostie/5420959">Code for widget</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-3" id="trello-ongoing">
        <div class="measurement-header">
          <h3 class="measurement-title">Trello</h3>
        </div>
        <div class="description">
            <p class="goal">Maximum three "Ongoing" tasks</p>
            <p>I use a Trello board with four sections for longer term projects that I am working on. </p>
            <p>I track ongoing projects in the "Ongoing" section.</p>
            <p>I have three "Icebox" sections for projects I'd like to start in the future: drawing projects, writing projects and any others.</p>
            <p class="code"><a href="https://gist.github.com/camilleldn/cda910d857f4c6225f75">Code for widget</a></p>
        </div>
      </div>
